    Deprecated. 
    Superseded by akka.cluster.metrics (in akka-cluster-metrics jar). Since 2.4.

    public class JmxMetricsCollector
extends java.lang.Object
implements MetricsCollector
    Loads JVM and system metrics through JMX monitoring beans.

    param: address The Address of the node being sampled param: decay how quickly the exponential weighting of past data is decayed
